(23, 1, '2016-06-18 18:57:21', '2016-06-18 18:57:21', '<div class="fusion-one-half fusion-layout-column fusion-spacing-yes box">\r\n<div class="fusion-column-wrapper">\r\n<div class="box-1">\r\n<h3 data-fontsize="18" data-lineheight="26">PERSONAL INJURY REPRESENTATION FOR TEXAS AND BEYOND</h3>\r\nWe represent victims of oil field accidents, medical malpractice, and vehicle accidents in West Texas and southeastern New Mexico as well as the Albuquerque metropolitan area. We''ve been helping our clients with their insurance claims and with litigation related to their personal injury cases since 1990, and if you been harmed in an accident, there''s a good chance we can help you do the same. Call Buckingham Barrera Law Firm to schedule a free consultation with a Midland personal injury attorney about your legal options for moving forward with your claim.\r\n<div class="btn-learn-more"><a href="http://localhost/buckingham/#">LEARN MORE</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="fusion-one-half fusion-layout-column fusion-column-last fusion-spacing-yes box">\r\n<div class="fusion-column-wrapper">\r\n<div class="box-2">\r\n<h3 data-fontsize="18" data-lineheight="26">HAVE YOU EXPERIENCED A CATASTROPHIC INJURY?</h3>\r\nThe financial and emotional price of a catastrophic injury is usually severe. In addition to preventing a victim from working, a serious car wreck or other accident can mean expensive medical bills that may seem impossible to take on. As an accident victim, however, you may be entitled to financial compensation if another person or party''s carelessness or recklessness played a role in causing your injuries. Contact a knowledgeable personal injury lawyer today if you or a member of your family has been severely injured in a car crash, an oil field pipeline explosion, or some other accident.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-18 18:57:21', '2016-06-18 18:57:21', '', 6, 